content.rendered:

  • Ultimate Speed and Agility Training Set – Comes with agility ladder with 4 metal pegs, 9 disc cones, running parachute & speed hurdles. Our set is made of durable and high quality materials that makes it perfect for coaches and athletes indoor & outdoor training in all sports: football, soccer, tennis, baseball or any sport that requires speed, quickness of the feet and vigilance.
  • TAKE YOUR ATHLEAthletic Performance to the Next Level – Run faster, jump higher & dig harder with resistance & HIIT training. Build explosive power as the resistance parachute for sprinting simulates sled training, creates air resistance and increases leg drive and top-end running speed. Proven & tested by professional athletes, coaches and trainers worldwide.
  • Develop strength, explosiveness and endurance: The resistance parachute creates drag which forces you to work harder, which in turn builds overall strength. Build speed and strength in one exercise. The resistance parachute for sprinting simulates sled training, creates air resistance and increases leg drive and top-end running speed
  • Easy Step by Step Training: Train yourself with our step-by-step training ebook: With a lifetime guarantee, your purchase of our speed set equipment comes with a fully illustrated ebook that shows you various training exercises for flexibility at every fitness level. Improve Your Speed, Agility, and Footwork Using the kit with our e-book to create a variety of exercises that will benefit your speed, agility, coordination, footwork, balance, and explosiveness.
  • Perfect Gift: Surprise your loved ones on their special days! Happiness will be unpredictable. Be a reason for others to smile. Present this wonderful and effective speed and agility set to your friends and family members who are looking for building their speed and agility. Gift it on their special occasions like birthdays, valentine, graduation, thanksgiving, etc.,
